description	"Jyn Erso

Class: Hero.
Class Summary: 
A speedy pistoleer with a stun gun. 

Weaponry:
- Truncheon (Can use Dual styles, cannot block any attacks)
- A180 (Based on Westar Pistol level 2, higher damage)
- A180 Ion Attachment *
- Sonic Grenade (2)

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- A180 Ion Attachment
- Based on Bowcaster level (3)
- Electrifies and knocks down enemies on direct hits
- 2 shots per clip, 20 shots total
- Magazine style reload

Attributes:
- Invisible to Force Sense
- Flipkick (2)
- Heal (3)

Inventory:
- Binoculars
- Portable Sentry Gun

Abilities:
- Combat Training [Jump 1]
- Dodge (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dash (2) [Alt Ability 1]

Jyn Erso was a human female soldier and former criminal who became a pivotal member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic when she led Rogue One in stealing the Death Star plans during the Battle of Scarif."